*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*   Record . . . . . M7102                                             *
*   Description  . . Combined Balance Code 1                           *
*   Product  . . . . Relationship Pricing                              *
*   Release  . . . . 5.0                                               *
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
SIZE=(22,67), ORIENT=(02,07)
WINDOW BOX
EASEL ON


                 Combined Balance Code 1 - Help

    This overrides the default balance in the combined balance
    calculation.  Valid entries are:

      00    Do not include this balance in the calculation.
      01    Current balance.
      02    Current customer collected.
      03    Current institution collected.
      04    Low balance.
      05    Average balance.
      06    Average collected balance.
      07    Commitment amount.
      08    Credit limit.
      09-15 Reserved.
      16-20 User-defined.  Interfaces must be modified to input
            user-defined balances.
                                                                _
    F12=Cancel                                            M02065S

EASEL OFF
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
FIELD=PFKEY,    PIC='X(01)', ATTR=(DISPLAY,HIDDEN)
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
